{"tid":621165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"足球名宿林守焯踢元老賽猝死","createTime":"2018-04-08T05:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:24:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69bc684c869e092d109ec72b7a3f0c75af7c50ae","tid":621165,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355159&d=dkkLZikCC5jk9TNU3iTsbBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=9eae1ec5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355159&h=df86562f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355159</a><br />\n<br />\n足球名宿林守焯踢元老賽猝死<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】香港足球名宿林守焯昨午參加足球元老賽時，突然暈倒球場上，經送院搶救後不治，終年68歲。友人事後紛紛於facebook留言悼念，有人稱讚林為「球壇鐵漢」，對他突然離世感到難過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180408/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180408%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=b5efe2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林守焯昏迷倒地，救護員為他急救，最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開賽5分鐘倒下<br />\n<br />\n林守焯早於70年代入選香港足球代表隊，曾效力加山、市政和東方，成為主力的中場球員，表現出色。據知他掛靴後仍不時參加小型足球比賽。<br />\n<br />\n現場為深水埗楓樹街球場，昨下午5時許，林在場參加元老賽「加山元老VS啟如」，他是加山元老的球員，未料賽事途中暈倒。據知當時球賽只開賽5分鐘，其間林突然失去知覺，身子直向後倒下。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，即場替林進行人工呼吸及心外壓急救，惟現場消息指，林當時已無反應，經送往明愛醫院搶救後證實不治。林守焯的友人一度在fb留言願他吉人天相，惟其後得悉噩耗，紛紛在fb留言悼念表示惋惜，盼他一路好走。有朋友更讚他是「球壇鐵漢」，並對他死於球場上致敬，形容是「英雄式辭世」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛"},{"pid":"5674e6d479d15357d6b8b3ded71cabe17b70ffdb","tid":621165,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307b05d90281695a5952878699fbc3a94a893ab3","tid":621165,"uid":105863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"戰死沙場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}